UI / API Test Pages
--------------------

html files for testing some of api's and API workflow verification.
These pages consume API responses from the backend and simulate real user flows
(e.g., card entry, redirect, callback handling).

## Files

1. razorpay_test.html - Triggers Razorpay Checkout.
Paste orderId + amount from /api/payment/initiate, complete payment in the Razorpay modal,
then copy the returned razorpayPaymentId/razorpaySignature into Postman for /api/payment/verify.

2. stripe_test.html - Mounts Stripe Elements card form.
Paste clientSecret + stripePaymentIntentId from /api/payment/initiate,
enter test card 4242 4242 4242 4242 and future date and any 3 digit number and confirm,
then copy the returned PaymentIntent ID into Postman for /api/payment/verify.